e matrices of coefficients. As a\nresult, we obtain that Carleson measure estimates for bounded null-solutions of\nnon-symmetric variable operators satisfying an $L^1$-Kenig-Pipher condition\noccur if and only if the boundary of the open set is uniformly rectifiable. Our\nresults generalize previous work in settings where quantitative connectivity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 13 Feb 2022 17:07:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-15"}
