ivistic elasticity based on\nthe relativistic right Cauchy-Green tensor or on the relativistic Cauchy\ndeformation tensor. The setting developed here will be further exploited for\nmodelling purpose in subsequent parts of the paper.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Feb 2022 08:59:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-15"}
