ion angle $\\phi_c$ on $\\Theta_w$,\nindicating that for gaseous flow with $\\Theta_w-1\\sim 1$ spanwise traveling\nwaves are predominant over a range of inclination angles $0 \\le \\phi \\le\n\\phi_c$ that is significantly wider than that predicted in the Boussinesq\napproximation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Feb 2022 09:20:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-15"}
