with stretch below a certain constant takes\n$\\widetilde \\Omega(n^{1/3})$ rounds even for labels of size $O(n^{2/3})$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Feb 2022 11:21:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-15"}
