ive hybrid detection method of\nFDIAs is established, considering the characteristic constraints of the\nparallel mode. A simulation system example of power CPS FDIAs verifies the\neffectiveness and accuracy of the method proposed in this paper.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Feb 2022 14:10:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-03"}
